Johnathan Cabot is a champion gymnast. 
In the tiny, yet savage, country of Parmistan, there is a perfect spot for a \"star wars\" site. For the US to get this site, they must compete in the brutal \"Game\". 
The government calls on Cabot, the son of a former operative, to win the game. Cabot must combine his gymnastics skills of the west with fighting secrets of the east and form GYMKATA!
